# UI/Demo rules

UI must prioritize engineering clarity and demo stability.

Required UI areas:
- Dashboard
- Rooms/devices view
- Event log
- Command console
- Clarification panel
- Debug trace
- Demo controls

UI must show:
- last user utterance
- normalized intent
- resolved entities
- system response
- current state
- event history

Prefer:
- simple readable layout
- deterministic demo flows
- obvious reset/replay controls

Avoid:
- overdesigned fragile UI
- hidden state mutations
- voice-only critical flows
